detailedDescription.articleBody: Koothuparambu firing was a police action on 25 November 1994. Later the incidence became in the name of Koothuparambu town. Kerala, India. The incident happened at Tellicherry Road in Kannur. The firing happened after the inauguration of the Co-operative Urban Bank’s evening branch.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: कूथुपराम्बु फायरिंग 25 नवंबर 1994 को एक पुलिस कार्रवाई थी, बाद में यह घटना कूथुपराम्बु शहर, केरल, भारत के नाम से हो गई, यह घटना कन्नूर के टेलिचेरी रोड पर हुई, फायरिंग को-ऑपरेटिव अर्बन बैंक की शाम की शाखा के उद्घाटन के बाद हुई।

detailedDescription.articleBody:
R. Annadurai is an Indian politician, belonging to the Communist Party of India.
R. Annadurai began his political career in the Democratic Youth Federation of India. He was the Madurai District Committee president of DYFI for ten years. He became the secretary of the Madurai District Committee of the CPI in 2008. Annadurai has been jailed several times in connection with different agitations.
